<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 06:20:02 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>拉杜卡努在韩国公开赛通过了斯特恩斯测试</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/raducanu-passes-stearns-test-korea-open-2024-09-18/</link><description>前美国公开赛冠军艾玛·拉杜卡努 (Emma Raducanu) 表示，她对自己的表现感到自豪，她在首尔举行的韩国公开赛首轮比赛中以 7-6(4) 7-6(5) 击败美国选手佩顿·斯特恩斯 (Peyton Stearns)，取得了 48 天以来的首场胜利。周二。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 05:44:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/raducanu-passes-stearns-test-korea-open-2024-09-18/</guid></item><item><title>印度在 MSCI 重要股票指数中首次超越中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/india-tops-china-first-time-ever-key-msci-equities-index-2024-09-18/</link><description>得益于稳定的经济增长和强劲的资金流动，印度在 MSCI 重要股票指数中首次超越中国。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 05:42:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/india-tops-china-first-time-ever-key-msci-equities-index-2024-09-18/</guid></item><item><title>北方房价超弱波及南方强区</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/ultra-weak-home-prices-northern-china-arrive-southern-powerhouses-2024-09-18/</link><description>预算紧张的中国购房者长期以来一直在寻找位于俄罗斯边境的前煤炭新兴城市鹤岗。现在，随着中国房地产危机的蔓延，鹤岗的地下室价格在较富裕的地区显现出来，对经济构成了新的威胁。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 05:35:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/ultra-weak-home-prices-northern-china-arrive-southern-powerhouses-2024-09-18/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，越南最高领导人林郑月娥下周将在美国会见谷歌和 Meta</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/vietnams-top-leader-lam-meet-google-meta-us-next-week-sources-say-2024-09-18/</link><description>两名知情人士告诉路透社，越南国家主席兼执政党共产党总书记苏林将于下周访问美国期间会见谷歌和 Meta 等多家美国公司的代表。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 05:09:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/vietnams-top-leader-lam-meet-google-meta-us-next-week-sources-say-2024-09-18/</guid></item><item><title>桥水基金的达里奥和新加坡 GIC 首席执行官对全球前景持谨慎态度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/bridgewaters-dalio-singapores-gic-chief-cautious-global-outlook-2024-09-18/</link><description>由于政治风险和不确定的全球增长前景，全球最大对冲基金创始人雷·达利奥(Ray Dalio)和新加坡主权财富基金GIC老板林秋吉(Lim Chow Kiat)对未来一年越来越谨慎。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 05:00:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/bridgewaters-dalio-singapores-gic-chief-cautious-global-outlook-2024-09-18/</guid></item><item><title>马来西亚苏丹将访华 寻求基础设施支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/malaysias-sultan-visit-china-eyes-infrastructure-support-2024-09-18/</link><description>中国外交部周三表示，马来西亚苏丹易卜拉欣将对中国进行为期四天的访问，来自南部柔佛州的礼仪统治者可能会寻求支持，以恢复加强与邻国新加坡互联互通的项目。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 04:09:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/malaysias-sultan-visit-china-eyes-infrastructure-support-2024-09-18/</guid></item><item><title>美元兑日元下跌，美联储迫在眉睫，亚洲股市陷入困境</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-18/</link><description>美元周三回吐了部分隔夜涨幅，而亚洲股市则陷入困境，因为交易员权衡美联储当天晚些时候大幅降息的可能性。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 02:19:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-18/</guid></item><item><title>台湾金阿波罗公司表示，它没有生产黎巴嫩爆炸中使用的寻呼机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/gold-apollo-says-it-did-not-make-pagers-used-lebanon-explosion-2024-09-18/</link><description>台湾金阿波罗公司周三表示，黎巴嫩爆炸中使用的寻呼机并非由该公司制造，而是由一家名为 BAC 的公司制造，该公司拥有使用其品牌的许可。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 02:10:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/gold-apollo-says-it-did-not-make-pagers-used-lebanon-explosion-2024-09-18/</guid></item><item><title>美联储决定前美元波动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-catches-footing-ahead-fed-2024-09-18/</link><description>美元周三波动，而日元收复部分失地，因投资者在预计将开始美国宽松周期的政策会议之前调整仓位。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 00:09:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-catches-footing-ahead-fed-2024-09-18/</guid></item><item><title>中国商务部长表示，电动汽车关税将损害德国和中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/ev-tariffs-will-cause-damage-germany-china-says-chinese-commerce-minister-2024-09-17/</link><description>中国商务部长表示，欧盟对电动汽车加征关税将“严重干扰”贸易和投资合作，对中德双方造成损害。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 23:55:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/ev-tariffs-will-cause-damage-germany-china-says-chinese-commerce-minister-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>据NHK报道，中国航母首次进入日本邻近海域</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-spots-chinese-carrier-group-sailing-off-its-east-coast-2024-09-17/</link><description>据日本公共广播公司NHK报道，周三，一艘中国航母首次暂时进入日本邻近海域，这一最新遭遇可能会进一步加剧邻国之间的紧张关系。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 23:54:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-spots-chinese-carrier-group-sailing-off-its-east-coast-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>独家：美国内部推动越南海底电缆计划远离中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/inside-us-push-steer-vietnams-subsea-cable-plans-away-china-2024-09-17/</link><description>了解谈判情况的消息人士称，美国敦促越南在到 2030 年建设 10 条新海底电缆的计划中避开中国电缆铺设公司 HMN Technologies 和其他中国公司。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 23:03:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/inside-us-push-steer-vietnams-subsea-cable-plans-away-china-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜一周内第二次发射短程弹道导弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-appears-have-fired-ballistic-missile-japan-says-2024-09-17/</link><description>韩国和日本表示，朝鲜周三向其东海岸发射了多枚短程弹道导弹，几天前平壤公布了一座铀浓缩设施，并誓言要加强其核武库。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 22:03:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-appears-have-fired-ballistic-missile-japan-says-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：美联储千钧一发——等待即将结束</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-09-17/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 21:51:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>上半场进球帮助阿尔希拉尔取得亚洲冠军联赛首场胜利</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/first-half-goals-ease-al-hilal-opening-asian-champions-league-win-2024-09-17/</link><description>周二，沙特阿拉伯的阿尔希拉尔队以 3-1 战胜卡塔尔的阿尔雷扬队，豪尔赫·热苏斯的球队在艾哈迈德·本·阿里体育场举行的亚洲冠军联赛精英赛联赛阶段开局不利。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 18:27:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/first-half-goals-ease-al-hilal-opening-asian-champions-league-win-2024-09-17/</guid></item></channel></rss>